271
00:18:14,220 --> 00:18:16,440
You okay with that?

272
00:18:16,440 --> 00:18:23,160
No, no. Actually, it's not all the time.

273
00:18:26,800 --> 00:18:28,240
I'll help you with the bike.

274
00:18:28,240 --> 00:18:30,080
No need.

275
00:18:31,020 --> 00:18:33,800
I'm flirting with you.

276
00:18:34,680 --> 00:18:36,900
