282
00:18:59,640 --> 00:19:04,600
But please, let me make a move.

283
00:19:05,580 --> 00:19:07,640
Got it?

284
00:19:24,680 --> 00:19:29,360
When I do it well enough,

285
00:19:30,840 --> 00:19:33,260
you can give in to me.

286
00:19:35,280 --> 00:19:39,100
But… for now, I just ask that...

287
00:19:40,220 --> 00:19:43,400
that we can stay together like this.

288
00:19:44,760 --> 00:19:47,240
Give me some time to flirt.

289
00:19:48,080 --> 00:19:51,040
I've prepared myself for this.

290
00:19:51,040 --> 00:19:53,600
Don't leave me just yet.

291
00:20:08,600 --> 00:20:11,860
Thi! What're you doing here?

292
00:20:14,120 --> 00:20:19,040
Just go! What are you lingering around for?

293
00:20:19,040 --> 00:20:21,120
I'm going home now.

294
00:20:21,120 --> 00:20:24,880
I'm too lazy to walk you to your dorm. I'm sleepy!

295
00:20:24,880 --> 00:20:26,720
Go ahead!

296
00:20:52,200 --> 00:20:55,620
Just get going! Your friends are waiting.

297
00:21:11,900 --> 00:21:13,740
What is it?

298
00:21:17,480 --> 00:21:19,560
Let's go. Get in the car.

299
00:21:35,100 --> 00:21:38,000
Hey. We are not drunk yet.

300
00:21:38,000 --> 00:21:41,020
